To build QuadRay engine demo under Linux
open console application and run:
    make -f RooT_make_x86.mk
for x86 architecture or
    make -f RooT_make_arm.mk
for ARM architecture. Maemo/scratchbox
cross-compilation environment was used.

To build QuadRay engine demo under Windows
open Visual C++ 6.0 (or later) and launch
    RooT_workspace.dsw
(agree to convert to newer versions), then press F5.

To build SIMD test framework under Linux
go to the "test" subfolder and run:
    make -f simd_make_x86.mk
for x86 architecture or
    make -f simd_make_arm.mk
for ARM architecture. Maemo/scratchbox
cross-compilation environment was used.

To build SIMD test framework under Windows
go to the "test" subfolder and launch
    simd_workspace.dsw
in Visual C++ 6.0 (or later),
(agree to convert to newer versions), then press F5.
